    <h1>White Hat SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">SEO practices that follow search engine guidelines and build rankings through <strong>genuine value, quality content, and earned authority</strong>. The opposite of black hat SEO — slower to show results but immune to penalties and durable across algorithm updates.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
